description:
A flimsy sword often used by children for fun and often
used for sparring.
name: Wooden Sword

description:
this Tomahawk is very well used and worn down. It also
doesn't seem to be holding together very well.
name: Flimsy Tomahawk

description:
A staff primarily used for those who struggle to walk
but it is said to have some magic properties.
name: Carved Staff

description:
A bow with quite a loose drawstring and can't fire
very far distances.
name: Lackstring Bow

description:
A largely carved stick with a stone arrow head mounted
at the top. It's quite effective at piercing skin.
name: Arrowhead Spear

description:
Gauntlets crafted from Rabbit hide and are held
together losely with leather string.
name: Hide Gauntlets

description:
A tool that simply is good skinning animals often used
while hunting to obtain hides.
name: Skinning Knife

description:
A well carved bow with a strong string, often used by
the people of Aria to hunt.
name: Hunter's Bow

description:
A staff that has been blessed by the spirits of the
Arian Burial grounds.
name: Ritual Staff
